Mangle Tools
============
A collection of tools for mangling meshes, shape keys, or curves.

Mesh Mangler
===========
A tool that moves verts around in a mesh.

Ani-Mangler
===========
Creates a shape key and moves around it's points randomly.
Does not (currently) work with curve objects, only meshes.


Curve Mangler
============
Randomly moves around points in a curve.
Works with nurbs, poly curves, and beziers.

